			<div id="post-837" class="hentry p1 post publish author-c4chaos category-kosmic-aperture category-religion category-spirituality y2008 m05 d05 h06">
				<h3 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.c4chaos.com/2008/05/the-new-atheists-wie/" title="Permalink to The New Atheists @ WIE" rel="bookmark">The New Atheists @ WIE</a></h3>
				<div class="entry-date"><abbr class="published" title="2008-05-05T13:34:45+0000">Monday, May 5th, 2008</abbr></div>
				<div class="entry-content">
<p>I just finished reading the featured article, Atheists with Attitude, on the latest issue of What is Enlightenment? magazine. As usual, WIE did a great job at presenting different perspectives, as well as the timeline of the evolution of Atheism. However, I was a bit disappointed with WIE&#8217;s take on the New Atheists for the [&hellip;]</p>
