			<div id="post-646" class="hentry p2 post publish author-c4chaos category-religion category-science y2008 m01 d27 h11 alt">
				<h3 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.c4chaos.com/2008/01/new-atheists-new-anti-dogmatists/" title="Permalink to New Atheists = New Anti-Dogmatists" rel="bookmark">New Atheists = New Anti-Dogmatists</a></h3>
				<div class="entry-date"><abbr class="published" title="2008-01-28T06:50:07+0000">Monday, January 28th, 2008</abbr></div>
				<div class="entry-content">
<p>This was so evident from the very start the &#8220;New Atheists&#8221; had been coined. But this article from Benjamin O&#8217;Donnell still puts it very succinctly. &#8220;What is strange is that, when one actually reads them, one gets the feeling that the real target of the &#8220;new atheists&#8221; isn&#8217;t religion at all. &#8220;Indeed, they all explicitly [&hellip;]</p>
