			<div id="post-604" class="hentry p3 post publish author-c4chaos category-politics category-religion category-science category-omni-peephole y2008 m01 d13 h02">
				<h3 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.c4chaos.com/2008/01/why-sam-harris-is-my-kind-of-new-atheist/" title="Permalink to Why Sam Harris is My Kind of New Atheist" rel="bookmark">Why Sam Harris is My Kind of New Atheist</a></h3>
				<div class="entry-date"><abbr class="published" title="2008-01-13T09:21:33+0000">Sunday, January 13th, 2008</abbr></div>
				<div class="entry-content">
<p>It&#8217;s no secret to readers of this blog that Sam Harris is my personal favorite among the New Atheists. I like them all, btw. Their books are part of my Creep Library collection. I admit that the tone and polemics used by Harris in his book, The End of Faith, could be a little harsh [&hellip;]</p>
